ver, something is different about the seemingly-naive little girl who has rubbed his lamp this time. For one thing, she\u2019s hired a strait-laced lawyer (Chris Parnell) to negotiate her wishes, and they might have a trick or two buried in the new contract\u2019s legalese\u2026.\n\nWritten and directed by award-winning VR creator Ethan Shaftel (KAIJU CONFIDENTIAL, EXTRAVAGANZA), AJAX ALL POWERFUL is an innovative VR comedy utilizing behind-the-scenes interactive triggers to create a fluid world of changing sizes and perspectives as the story progresses from the lamp to the real world, and beyond, ", "short_description": "Ajax (Henry Winkler) is a foul-mouthed genie addicted to the human souls he collects after tricking gullible masters. But something is different about the little girl who found his lamp this time: she's hired a lawyer to negotiate her wishes. "}]}, "developer_name": "easyAction", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://o8dy6wafc.bkt.clouddn.com/VeeR-PrivacyPolicy.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VeeR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://AjaxAllPowerful.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1008279844328894"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["NARRATIVE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "302476258990607"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974732_282588090957071_5341492191533598626_n